{"tid":1836450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美指中國未能限期前將北韓勞工遣回國　違反聯合國決議","createTime":"2020-01-23T08:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T17:20:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e374cb0d28d2d158053f6fbe637582e13f34c1b5","tid":1836450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"美指中國未能限期前將北韓勞工遣回國 違反聯合國決議<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504404-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504404-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=644ed155\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504404-20200123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aaecdc83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504404-20200123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國指中國未能在限期前將北韓勞工遣返回國，違反聯合國制裁北韓的決議。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國安理會2017年通過決議，要求所有國家在上月22日前，驅逐所有北韓勞工，以阻截北韓發展彈道導彈及核武的收入來源。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美方估計，平壤每年從近10萬名海外勞工，獲得超過5億美元收入，其中有5萬人及3萬人分別在中國及俄羅斯工作。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n路透社引述美國國務院一名高級官員說，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大部分國家都有按決議遣返北韓勞工，但暗指中國一直未採取有關措施。</span></span></strong>官員又表示，華府仍然期望與北韓恢復核談判。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，華府上星期宣布制裁兩個北韓實體，包括一間總部設於中國、為北韓人提供住宿的公司。"},{"pid":"e77920e7f2cb75883a005942e51a6f9c450325c9","tid":1836450,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"長任理事國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68671d4f63f13a6cd8e3ee19732a03eb905cb9b4","tid":1836450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}